Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your trusted bowling alley. My name is Alex. How may I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I’m having some issues with my last billing statement.

I’d be happy to help you with that. May I have your name, please?

Sure, it’s Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Can you please provide the billing account number associated with your account? It's usually a six-digit number.

Yes, it’s three four five six two one.

Great, thank you. Could you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number for security purposes?

It’s nine eight seven six.

Thank you for confirming, Jamie. I can see the details now. It seems there was a small issue with the last statement which I'll go ahead and correct for you.

That’s a relief. Thank you for sorting it out, Alex.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for your patience. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to call us anytime. Have a great day!
